<para xml:id="C14.S18.SS4.p1">

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="1" sentence-num-in-section="18" xml:id="C14.S18.SS4.p1.s1">
For collections of sums involving associated Legendre functions, seeHansen (1975, pp. 367–377, 457–460, and 475),Erdélyi et al. (1953a, §3.10), Gradshteyn and Ryzhik (2000, §8.92),Magnus et al. (1966, pp. 178–184), andPrudnikov et al. (1990, §§5.2, 6.5).
</sentence>

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="2" sentence-num-in-section="19" xml:id="C14.S18.SS4.p1.s2">
See also §18.18 and (34.3.19).
</sentence>

</para>
 
